<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2em;
        }

            .buttons a {
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 1em 2em;
                background-color: #00b131;
                color: black;
                font-weight: bold;
                border-radius: 10px;
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            }

                .buttons a:hover {
                    background-color: #00ff00;
                }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Bem Vindo(a) ao CP2!</h1>
        <p>O que você deseja gerenciar hoje?</p>
        <div class="buttons">
            <a asp-controller="Moto" asp-action="MotoView">Motos</a>
            <a asp-controller="Patio" asp-action="PatioView">Pátio</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 